{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","text":"NSArray<id<MLNAnnotation>>","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotations","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The array of annotation objects to remove. Objects in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"array must conform to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotations"}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removing annotation objects dissociates them from the map view entirely,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"preventing them from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"call this method only when you want to hide or delete the given annotations."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes an array of annotations from the map view, deselecting any selected"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotations in the array."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotations:"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapvi